    <title>Mathematical Constants</title>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><computeroutput>M_PI, M_SQRT2 etc.</computeroutput></para><para><bold>#include</bold> &lt;<ref refid="mathutil_8hxx_source" kindref="compound">vigra/mathutil.hxx</ref>&gt;</para><para>Since mathematical constants such as <computeroutput>M_PI</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>M_SQRT2</computeroutput> are not officially standardized, we provide definitions here for those compilers that don&apos;t support them.</para><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="preprocessor">#ifndef<sp/>M_PI</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>define<sp/>M_PI<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>3.14159265358979323846</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#endif</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#ifndef<sp/>M_SQRT2</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>define<sp/>M_2_PI<sp/><sp/><sp/>0.63661977236758134308</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#endif</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#ifndef<sp/>M_PI_2</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>define<sp/>M_PI_2<sp/><sp/><sp/>1.57079632679489661923</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#endif</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#ifndef<sp/>M_PI_4</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>define<sp/>M_PI_4<sp/><sp/><sp/>0.78539816339744830962</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#endif</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#ifndef<sp/>M_SQRT2</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>define<sp/>M_SQRT2<sp/><sp/>1.41421356237309504880</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#endif</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#ifndef<sp/>M_EULER_GAMMA</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>define<sp/>M_EULER_GAMMA<sp/><sp/>0.5772156649015329</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="preprocessor">#endif</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>    </detaileddescription>
